title: 安田記念の後に・勝ってばばんばー

text_block_list.text: Ikuno Dictus has been defeated by Matikanetannhauser!
Ikuno Dictus shows her frustration, but influenced by Matikanetannhauser, whose catchphrase is 'Next time for sure,' she firmly looks ahead.
Later, the two visit a super sento (public bath) at Ikuno Dictus's suggestion.
They thoroughly recover from fatigue and prepare for the next race!
